OL,3,COne-punch attacker back in prison
OL,4,Cafter victim's death seven years on
OL,6,FA former football hooligan who was
OL,7,Fjailed for attacking a man at a party
OL,8,Fhas been returned to prison following
OL,9,Fthe victim's death seven years later.
OL,11,FSimon Hackett was left brain damaged
OL,12,Fafter being punched by Jordan Docherty
OL,13,Fat Buttershaw Lane Working Men's Club
OL,14,Fin Bradford in 2015.
OL,16,FDocherty, who was 20 at the time, was
OL,17,Fsentenced in 2016 to four years in
OL,18,Fyouth custody for causing grievous
OL,19,Fbodily harm.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
