OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774008171
OL,3,COne-punch attacker back in prison
OL,4,Cafter victim's death seven years on
OL,6,FBut Mr Hackett, who was 35 at the time
OL,7,Fof the attack, suffered a decline in
OL,8,Fhealth and died in 2022.
OL,10,FDocherty, of Studley Avenue,
OL,11,FButtershaw, Bradford, has now been
OL,12,Fgiven an additional sentence of 15
OL,13,Fmonths after admitting manslaughter.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
