PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774008171
OL,3,COne-punch attacker back in prison
OL,4,Cafter victim's death seven years on
OL,6,FSentencing Docherty at Leeds Crown
OL,7,FCourt, the judge, Recorder Guy Kearl
OL,8,FKC, said of Mr Hackett's family: "No
OL,9,Fsentence that I can pass will be
OL,10,Fsufficient to compensate their loss -
OL,11,Fnot just from the death of Simon
OL,12,FHackett, but the seven years watching
OL,13,Fhis decline.
OL,15,F"From the date you punched him, to the
OL,16,Fday he died, their lives have been
OL,17,Fdevastated, never to be the same."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
