PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774008171
OL,3,COne-punch attacker back in prison
OL,4,Cafter victim's death seven years on
OL,6,FProsecutor Matthew Bean told the court
OL,7,Fthe incident happened after a
OL,8,Fdisagreement between Mr Hackett and
OL,9,FDocherty's cousin.
OL,11,FDocherty knocked Mr Hackett out with a
OL,12,Fsingle punch, causing him a fractured
OL,13,Fskull and swelling to his brain.
OL,15,FHe remained in hospital and later
OL,16,Frequired round-the-clock care before
OL,17,Fhis death after developing pneumonia.
OL,19,FDocherty was jailed again in May 2023,
OL,20,Ffor three years, after leaving a man
OL,21,Fin a coma following another attack.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
