PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1774008171
OL,3,COne-punch attacker back in prison
OL,4,Cafter victim's death seven years on
OL,6,FMr Bean said he had previous
OL,7,Fconvictions for football-related
OL,8,Fviolence.
OL,10,FNick Johnson, mitigating for Docherty,
OL,11,Fsaid: "Nothing that I can say on
OL,12,Fbehalf of Mr Docherty can right the
OL,13,Fwrong that was perpetrated almost 11
OL,14,Fyears ago... it's important that I
OL,15,Fexpress his profound apologies."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
